name: Alaska - Chugach
description:
This photo was shot deep in the Chugach Mountain range in Valdez, Alaska.

This is a high quality canvas print that is ready to hang on your wall. 
1 ¼" depth, with a fully finished back & pre-intstalled hinged hanging hardware.

Choose from one of the three sizes below. 

***Shipping included***

*Please allow 1-2 weeks for printing and shipping of the product.

Teddy Hoffman is a Chicago based photographer & cinematographer. Check out thvisuals.com for info.

name: Alaska - Fishing boats
description:
This photo was shot in the town of Valdez, Alaska at the fishing harbor. This was a typical "down day" in Alaska where it snowed all day and visibility was extremely low. Valdez's Prince William Sound is a premier fishing destination, open year-round, offering all species of salmon, rock fish, ling cod, and some of the most accessible big halibut in Alaska.  

This is a high quality canvas print that is ready to hang on your wall. 
1 ¼" depth, with a fully finished back & pre-intstalled hinged hanging hardware.
